    "body": "- `nvim --version`: NVIM v0.5.0-dev+1116-gbda12927b\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce using `nvim -u NORC`\r\n\r\n```\r\nnvim -u NORC\r\n:set nowrap\r\n5000ik<ESC>\r\n:lua ns_id = vim.api.nvim_create_namespace(\"foo\")\r\n:lua vim.api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, ns_id, 0, 1, { virt_text={{'gg', 'String'}}, virt_text_pos='overlay'})\r\n$\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nWhen scrolling right, the overlay virtual text stays in the same place relative to the window.\r\n\r\n### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nIt should scroll with the rest of the text",
